16816, "Reconnaissance Lourde"

16817, "(fr)Nankam Aeronautical"

16818, "(fr) "

16819, "(fr)The Aurora is a heavy reconnaissance fighter designed to replace the Loki in its intended role of scouting, interception and space superiority. The Aurora is a swift fighter and carries several advanced avionics and sensor systems to assist in the gathering of information. However, the added equipment has produced a heavy hull, limiting the combat manoeuverability of the design. Federation fighter pilots treat Auroras as priority targets, due to their ability to transmit precision jump telemetry to GTVA capital ships, provide additional targeting data to Alliance fighters, and call in subspace missile strikes."

